index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF HOUSING AND URBAN DEVELOPMENT
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (No. Wash. R-5) authorizing a contract for sale of land, special warranty deeds and redevelopment contract for property in Blocks 19 and 22 of H. L. Yesler's First Addition to the City of Seattle, Block 5 of Hill Tract Addition to the City of Seattle and in vacated South Washington Street as a site for a prototype housing system under Operation Breakthrough.
